{"tid":1356693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗反黑警勾結行動方針","createTime":"2019-07-23T14:29:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T17:48:41.000Z","uid":253016,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4354506c11060e31f4745b3c24371d9159f41e43","tid":1356693,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:29:44.000Z","msg":"第一點最重要<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">象徵意義</span></span></strong> 遠大於 實際破壞<br />\n共產黨搵黑警勾結 佢想要既結果係香港人陷入恐懼而屈服<br />\n今次入元朗既話 目標一定係對黑警勾結行動表示抵抗<br />\n如果行動成功可以挽回香港人既士氣 非常重要<br />\n所以點都好 一定要針對警黑勾結行動示威<br />\n<br />\n第二點<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">旗 BANNER 大聲公 </span></span>要帶多D 示威既時候以壯聲勢 可以幫手足壯膽 同時可以阻嚇鄉黑進犯 <br />\nBANNER同旗可以針對警黑勾結製作<br />\n<br />\n第三點 <br />\n唔一定要所謂&quot;燒村&quot; 正如第一點所講 今次目的係要表明心志 挽回手足同其他港豬既士氣<br />\n絕對唔向恐怖屈服 但係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">示威唔係尋仇鬥毆 少打架 避免入小巷窄路<br />\n多在象徵物 地標做抗議行為 而且要公告天下</span></span><br />\n<br />\n第四點 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">多聯絡記者傳媒 網紅</span></span> <br />\n一來可以保護示威人士<br />\n二來亦可以增加抗爭注目度 向外表明抗爭不會停止既心志<br />\n<br />\n第五點 要帶多D防身用品 唔係自己地頭 亦唔排除有人想突登搞事 唔好落單<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總括黎講 今次行動主要目的係打破共產黨拿手既恐懼陷阱 提升士氣<br />\n以最低代價換取行動成功<br />\n時間唔多 希望幫到手<br />\n<br />\n同意幫手推比手足睇唔該"},{"pid":"8d81c73b40f6623b62075a1ae9fc31288adacde0","tid":1356693,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:29:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7175356ea3eacc048a4c0ff4aa8761391c9cb47f","tid":1356693,"uid":237077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:30:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7nBtCFX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7nBtCFX.jpg&h=a3d5aa01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47b667286a6ec190225ba94856f3d8dfafe03126","tid":1356693,"uid":279085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:30:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzfNKZRPQHZk&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4YRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=fdb4bd8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk</a>"},{"pid":"20e2bab515742ab21996b3a8702fbc9076fcb54d","tid":1356693,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:32:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73734bff60cf627fd1b499474ba5c0b9418413ac","tid":1356693,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:33:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b3e049706a44e3f90803cfa8c216f4810c1fb57","tid":1356693,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:37:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0359b649c7747f3ecdeeee2edf72e390171d1447","tid":1356693,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7dff2f7bbb7ef8de05d48d2857c99bcf35aa8a","tid":1356693,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:20:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffe4e2237754df2c7229db89bef323c181f890ae","tid":1356693,"uid":48220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:21:20.000Z","msg":"麻煩727去嘅巴絲睇一睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「長期置頂」727元朗反鄉黑遊行終極攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356464\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356464</a>"},{"pid":"29bae3f4a00252a81536fe009f7282c0c067cd2f","tid":1356693,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T